metadata.name: Trihexafobia
metadata.description:
Paulina Koalatovska - Trihexafobia 
4403*6000
2020

Trihexaphobia is the irrational and disproportionate fear of the number 666. I grew up in a religious family, where fear and guilt were the way to educate, punishment the only way to atone for sins acquired by inheritance. This work is about learned fear, about the panic before emancipation.


This is my first NFT, IÂ´m so excited to share my work in this community.
